{"title":"谒阴山岩画","authors":["白朝蓉"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":11,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"谒阴山岩画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白朝蓉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向天之涯三鞠躬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向地之沿九叩头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岩画在阴阳裂变中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崛起中华祖先的遗嘱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石刀凿刻的古老往事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管冰冷时火烧火燎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管沉默时雷鸣电闪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我能读懂无字的史诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为历史的五彩泡沫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在民族忠魂的心扉化蝶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流动与不流动的白云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总会变成雨滴掉下来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游弋骑射的陡峭山岭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸膛是土黄色的花岗岩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳和月亮转动轮子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辗出意识皱折的风俗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啼饥于狩猎崇拜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号寒于天体崇拜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横祸于神灵崇拜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不孕于生殖崇拜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从昆仑山口到阴山山麓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从猎猎朔风到滔滔江水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万幅岩画像疲惫的星群"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一万年白云苍狗无痕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五千年改朝换代有序"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找不到刀币式的衣钵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"查不出女娲式的姓名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匈奴人胡马如云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敕勒人歌谣如水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突厥人弓箭如铁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女真人文字如绳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒙古人版图如鞍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汉家人诗词如汤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已再现的无法重复"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已消失的反倒永恒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且听蔡文姬的胡笳曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且看郦道元的《水经注》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岩画，哲人般缄默"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羝鼓，将军般吞吐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无须化验血型"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无须鉴定基因"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无须寻根访祖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无须求坟问典"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共枕大漠孤烟弯与直"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共饮黄河波峰苦与甜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"５"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也得从岩画中走出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也得从岩浆中化入"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使跨上地磁列车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重读穿Ｔ恤衫的犄角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华民族缘与寰球同庚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：内蒙古自治区文联）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}